import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Link } from 'docz';
import { Analytics } from './Analytics';
Analytics.init();

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"getting-started"}}>{`Getting started`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Getting started with graphql editor is very easy.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"using-graphql-editor-component"}}>{`Using GraphQL Editor Component`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-sh"}}>{`\$ npm i graphql-editor
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Navigate to `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"./Editor"}}>{`Editor`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"development"}}>{`Development`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-sh"}}>{`\$ git clone https://github.com/slothking-online/graphql-editor
\$ cd graphql-editor
\$ npm i
\$ npm run start
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`It will run sandboxed environment with basic GraphQL Editor and code.
Feel free to contribute or file an issue.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"visual-editor-usage"}}>{`Visual Editor Usage`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`You can import your GraphQL Schema or create your own from scratch. To create your schema you have 2 ways:`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Code schema in code editor`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Draw it with spacebar menu`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`If you dont know GraphQL language here are some good resources to start:`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://www.howtographql.com/"}}>{`https://www.howtographql.com/`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://graphql.github.io/learn/"}}>{`https://graphql.github.io/learn/`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
